OL,3,CClean-up operation begins in
OL,4,CPontypridd after Storm Bert damage
OL,6,FResidents and businesses in Pontypridd
OL,7,Fare working to clean up the
OL,8,Fdevastation caused by Storm Bert
OL,9,Fflooding.
OL,11,FHomes across Rhondda Cynon Taf were
OL,12,Fhit by torrential downpours of rain at
OL,13,Fthe weekend, amid fears of a more
OL,14,Fsignificant impact than the
OL,15,Fdestruction of Storm Dennis in 2020.
OL,17,FBetween 200 and 300 properties in the
OL,18,Farea were affected by flooding, with
OL,19,Flocal leaders expressing surprise at
OL,20,Fthe extent of the rainfall.
