OL,6,FRhondda Cynon Taf County Borough
OL,7,FCouncil, South Wales Fire and Rescue,
OL,8,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) and
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police declared a major
OL,10,Fincident for the borough on Sunday, 24
OL,11,FNovember, with record river levels
OL,12,Frecorded on the River Taff on Saturday
OL,13,Fnight.
OL,15,FAs the sun rose on Rhondda Cynon Taf
OL,16,Fon Monday, it revealed a familiar
OL,17,Fscene, with homes flooded, cars
OL,18,Fdestroyed and valuables damaged beyond
OL,19,Frepair.
