OL,6,FKevin Kidner lives on Sion Street, one
OL,7,Fof the residential roads flooded for
OL,8,Fthe second time in less than five
OL,9,Fyears. His people-carrier was already
OL,10,Fhalf-way underwater before he could
OL,11,Fsave it.
OL,13,FHe told ITV Wales: "I looked out about
OL,14,F7 o'clock and it looked calm. About
OL,15,Fhalf an hour later my neighbour came
OL,16,Frunning up the street saying (the
OL,17,Friver) had broken its banks.
OL,19,F"I moved my wife's car and when I came
OL,20,Fback (my car) was already up to the
OL,21,Fwheel arches, about 3ft under.
