OL,6,FChris Hadfield, assistant chief fire
OL,7,Fofficer at South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService, told ITV Wales the volume of
OL,9,Fcalls was so high that fire service
OL,10,Fstaff from other services were drafted
OL,11,Fin to help respond.
OL,13,FHe said: "We had about 21 fire and
OL,14,Frescue services helping out with our
OL,15,Fcalls. Around 9am (on Sunday 24
OL,16,FNovember) we recognised there were a
OL,17,Flot of communities in need across the
OL,18,Fwhole of south Wales and we declared a
OL,19,Fmajor incident.
