OL,6,F"That allows us to inform our partners
OL,7,Fthat this is no longer business as
OL,8,Fusual and that we need assistance from
OL,9,Fa multi-agency point of view.
OL,11,F"It dawned on us very quickly that we
OL,12,Fneeded to get help out there to our
OL,13,Fcommunities, which we did to in a
OL,14,Fmulti-agency way.
OL,16,F"Today is about reaching out to our
